dct_alternative_sm: Il vero disegno di Vicovaro occvpato da Imperiali et recvperato dalla Chiesa a di XIIII Febraro, MDLVII
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially and by shading.
Shows siege of Vicobaro, with attacking artillery, armies, buildings (including castle), figures, sourrounding topography, vegetation.
